• Shift4 will continue to be compensated for all CardConnect gateway transactions on all processors.

• Shift4 will provide CardConnect with the necessary reporting to support revenue share reconciliation.

• **Shift4 will not continue a reseller relationship for a merchant that ports away from CardConnect to
Shift4 Payments.This does not apply to merchants boarded before the 1eseller becomes a Shift4
Payments reseller.**
• Shift4 acknowledges that its other divisions (e.g. HTG, Merchant Link, etc.) may enter into reseller
agreements that result in the movement of merchants from CardConnect to other merchant acquirers.

Please let me know if the above is consistent with your understanding.
Thank you,

Jared
